location.fullValue: The Yacht Club On The Intracoastal

data.description: Immerse yourself in the epitome of coastal living in this stunning turn-key 2-bed, 2-bath villa. Located just steps from the Intracoastal, this gated community rests along the widest part of the waterway. With abundant natural light, this meticulously maintained home features a split open floorplan boasting an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, all new porcelain tile flooring (no carpet!), plus a flex room that can be used as a gym, lounge area, playroom, or more. The community is an oasis of amenities, including a clubhouse, fitness center, pickleball courts, shuffleboard, and a resort-style waterfront pool. Truly a must-see hidden gem property that rarely becomes available
